claude-agent-sdk (Rust)

This crate is a Rust port of the session-reading functionality of Anthropic's
`claude-agent-sdk` for Python:

    https://github.com/anthropics/claude-agent-sdk-python

Specifically, it ports the filesystem session-reading logic found in
`src/claude_agent_sdk/_internal/sessions.py` and the accompanying test suite in
`tests/test_sessions.py`. The live-streaming client (`query()`, subprocess
transport) and the async `SessionStore` backend are intentionally NOT ported —
this crate reads local `~/.claude/projects/**/*.jsonl` history only.

